data.description: Pride of ownership abounds in this fantastic family home in lovely Fairhaven! This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath, like new, beauty rests on an over size lot in a quiet cul de sac. Master down and two bedrooms up , plus a flex space / loft. Kitchen is open to living area with soaring high ceilings. Wood look luxury vinyl plank in main areas. Four sides brick / stone. Includes full gutters and in ground sprinkler system.
